    <newsTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[Play in Competitive Tournaments]]></Value>
    </newsTitle>
    <newsExcerpt>
      <Value><![CDATA[Show off your Moo Family skills in weekly tournaments and win LAIT tokens and rare collectibles.]]></Value>
    </newsExcerpt>
    <newsBody>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Compete with players around the world in seasonal MooRash and MooSoccer tournaments. Top scorers earn LAIT tokens, badges, and exclusive in-game items.</p><p>Registration opens every Friday. Brackets are released Saturday morning.</p>]]></Value>
